data.text:
If you have any comments or questions or if there is anything I or my staff can do to help you, please don't hesitate to contact us. We can be reached in our Portland Office at 207-774-5019.

Office Locations

Portland Office

2 Portland Fish Pier, Suite 304

Portland, ME 04101

(207) 774-5019

Fax: (207) 871-0720 Waterville Office

1 Silver Street

Waterville, ME 04901

(207) 873-5713

Fax: (207) 873-5717 Washington, DC Office

2354 Rayburn House Office Building

Washington DC 20515

(202) 225-6116

Send Me an Email— Fill out this form to send an email to the Representative.

Newsletter Signup — Subscribe to receive email updates on our work in Congress.

Help with a Federal Agency — If you are working with a federal agency and are not receiving an answer in a timely fashion, or you feel you've been treated unfairly, our office may be able to assist you resolve the problem or get more information.

Meeting Request — Fill out this form to request a meeting with our office or the Representative.

Event Request — Fill out this form to invite the Representative to attend an event.

Visiting Washington, DC — Our staff can assist you with obtaining tickets for tours of the U.S. Capitol building and other Washington, DC attractions.

Press Requests —Members of the media looking to contact Congresswoman Pingree should visit this page.
